17 December 2003   V1-8
      Changes for the port to GEM8.5 (EPICS 3.13.9).

03 January 2006    V1-8-1
       Change default number of leap seconds to 33.0.

11 January 2006   V1-8-2
      Modified timelibInstall to allow compiling for EPICS releases other
      than GEM8.5

11 January 2006   V1-8-4
      Modified to add the June 2012 leap second.

<... time passes ...>

19 December 2017  V1-9-7
      Merged in changes to timeCheck changing the way we acquire the current
      time, and how we derive taiNTP.

      Also, changed timeSeq.st to ignore offset larger than 5µs, which
      for us typically only leads to spurious alarms and bad health condition,
      confusing the science users.

27 December 2017  V1-9-8
      Updated configure/RELEASE to depend on the 1-6-6 version of the
      Bancomm support module.

28 December 2017  V1-9-9
      Updated configure/RELEASE to depend on the 1-6-7 version of the
      Bancomm support module, which fixes the TZ bug

28 December 2017  V1-9-10
      Matt realized that there were some changes missing for release V1-9-7,
      reintroducing the spurious bad health condition. Fixed.

28 December 2017  V1-9-11
      Fix the configure/RELEASE file, which became unusable for production
      while merging the changes for he previous release.
